sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Cl as 클라이언트
    participant API as POST /api/upload
    participant R2 as Cloudflare R2

    Cl->>API: { filename, contentType, size }
    API->>API: size ≤ MAX_UPLOAD_SIZE(10MB) 검증
    API->>R2: presigned PUT URL 생성 (expiresIn 300s)
    API-->>Cl: { presignedUrl, key, publicUrl }
    Cl->>R2: PUT presignedUrl (파일 직접 전송)
    R2-->>Cl: 200 OK
    Cl->>API: publicUrl을 DB에 저장
